          <title>Postponed NASA, Space X Falcon 9 mission rescheduled for Friday</title>
          <description><![CDATA[NASA and SpaceX rescheduled the launch of their Falcon 9 rocket rescue mission to the International Space Station for Friday. They were unable to launch on Wednesday due to issues with equipment on the ground, and opted to scrub a Thursday launch attempt due to weather.]]></description>
